Class Road

java.lang.Object
Road
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Road>
public class Road
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Road>
The purpose of Road is to serve as the edge structure for the Graph and TownGraphManager classes, using Town as the vertexes. I swear I have not copied any code.
Author:
Nicholas A. Baker
